mcp-multiplexer.js — stdio MCP aggregator (IDE ↔ children)

class MCPMultiplexer
  constructor(proxyManager)→void|init request map, tools map
  listen()→void|start all child servers, read IDE stdin line-by-line
  sendToIde(msg)→void|write JSON-RPC to stdout, broadcast to monitors
  handleIdeMessage(msg)→void|route IDE request to appropriate handler
  aggregateList(ideRequestId,method,key)→Promise<void>|collect list from all children, merge, respond
  handleChildMessage(serverName,msg)→void|route child response back to IDE with original ID

PROTOCOL:
  initialize → respond with capabilities, forward to all children
  initialized → forward to all children
  tools/list → aggregate from all children, build toolsMap
  prompts/list → aggregate from all children
  resources/list → aggregate from all children
  tools/call → lookup toolsMap, forward to target server with rewritten ID

PATTERNS: ID rewriting|tool→server routing map|list aggregation
DEPS: mcp-proxy.js (MCPProxyManager)
